---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Namaste!</h1>
			<p>
				I'm <strong>Rupika</strong>, currently pursuing my <strong>third year of B.Tech in Computer Science and Engineering (Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning)</strong>.
			</p>
			<p>
				I am passionate about learning new technologies and continuously improving my technical skills. I enjoy exploring the latest advancements in AI, machine learning, and software development.
			</p>
			<p>
				Beyond technology, I have a deep interest in researching ancient temples, their history, architecture, and cultural significance. I love discovering how India's rich heritage connects with science, engineering, and tradition.
			</p>
			<p>
				Welcome to my blog, where I share my learning journey, technology insights, and fascinating discoveries about ancient temples.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
